<H2>
Our Online Omaha-Ponca Language Materials</H2>

<IMG SRC="dot5.gif"><b><A HREF="
http://www.native-languages.org/omaha_words.htm
">Omaha-Ponca Vocabulary</a></b><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Our list of vocabulary words in the Omaha-Ponca language, with comparison to words in other Siouan languages.
<BR>

<h2>
<A name="materials">Omaha-Ponca</a> Dictionaries, Audio Tapes and Language Resources
</u><BR><font size=2>Our organization earns a commission from any book bought through these links</font>
</h2>

<IMG SRC="dot5.gif"><b><A HREF="
http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/0781244382/natilangofthe-20
">The Cegiha Language (Omaha and Ponka)</a></b> <IMG SRC="star.gif" ALT="*"> <b><A HREF="
http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/0403036755/natilangofthe-20
">Omaha and Ponca Letters</a></b> <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Collections of annotated Omaha-Ponca texts for sale online.
